description: Kauai, HI This food truck is cooking up some tasty sunny day sandwiches on the beautiful island of Kauai. Try a local favorite like the loco moco breakfast item which typically includes a beef hamburger patty, a fried egg, and brown gravy all atop a bed of white rice. In addition, they also offer burgers, tacos, main plates and a variety of fresh locally caught seafood.
name: Kauai Food Truck
